headline: NASA plans space shuttle launch on July 13
description: NASA said on Thursday it planned to launch the space shuttle Discovery on July 13, the first shuttle mission since the Columbia disaster in 2003. (Reuters)
articleBody: NASA said on Thursday it planned to launch the space shuttle Discovery on July 13, the first shuttle mission since the Columbia disaster in 2003. (Reuters)
